<plot>Money trouble causes struggling couple Colleen and Chad to temporarily split. Seeking refuge at Maqz's place (a spoiled rich, 20 something agoraphobic), Chad enters into a game of "How Much". (i.e. How much would it take for you to get naked in public? eat a cockroach? etc.) They decide on a bet involving Colleen, a violent death, and a video spy camera that twists a triangle of deadly deceit where they each discover exactly how much they can take, and then push it further.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?248184</url></doc>
